targets.queryText:
SELECT CAST(strftime('%s', 'now', '-1 minute') as INTEGER) as time, 4 as value
    WHERE time >= 1234 and time < 134567

SELECT CAST(strftime('%s', 'now', '-1 minute') as INTEGER) as time, 4 as value 
WHERE time >= $__from / 1000 and time < $__to / 1000
